winning_structure.name: UBX-NAV-TIMETRUSTED
winning_structure.description: External trusted time information. This message contains information about external trusted time received via assistance data (UBX-MGA-INI-TIME_UTC or UBX-MGA-INI-TIME_GNSS).

fields.name: refSys
fields.description:
Reference time system (all the GNSS system supported by UBX-MGA-INI-TIME_GNSS except Glonass)
• 0: None
• 1: GPS Time
• 2: Galileo System Time (GST)
• 3: Beidou System Time (BDT)
• 15: NavIC System Time

bits.name: trustedTime
bits.description: 1 = Valid initial and propagated trusted time (iniWno, iniTow, finiTow, iniTAcc, propWno, propTow, fPropTow and propTAcc)

bits.name: deltaTimeValid
bits.description: 1 = Valid delta time (deltas and deltaMs) between current estimated time and the propagated trusted time

fields.name: iTOW
fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch. See section iTOW timestamps in the integration manual for details.

fields.name: propWno
fields.description: Week number propagating the initial trusted time

fields.name: propTow
fields.description: Time of week propagating the initial trusted time

fields.name: deltas
fields.description: Integer seconds of delta time (current estimated time minus propagated trusted time)

fields.name: deltaMs
fields.description: Integer milliseconds of delta time (current estimated time minus propagated trusted time)
